					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">- I'm aware of <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=3396#3396" class="postlink">APU timings</a> and ya, the wiki was missing such table. Anyway, the test reads $4015 two times. The first time, the APU is clocked in the 2nd cycle of the following AND instruction. The second time, the APU is clocked right after reading $4015. Both return 1 because the remaining length is still 1.</div>

